”The mother said she wasn't the only parent who had been singled out by authorities at the scene, which she characterized as chaotic. She claims she witnessed officers tackling a parent to the ground and pepper-spraying another. When a third father approached a school bus with children on board to pick up his child, officers tasered him, she added. “They didn’t do that to the shooter, but they did that to us,” Gomez informed the Journal, referring to herself and other parents. “That’s how it felt.”Happy memorial day.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/aBS40EL</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>This is what happens when you block the tram in Sheffield</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/S62AfeT</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bdXoW4f.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/S62AfeT</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Uraza111]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>To Cower And Flee...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/KuOBDqm</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Wy6VlxR.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/KuOBDqm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DrForester]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Her name is Angeli Rose Gomez</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Y1wEOX1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/J0YyKlM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Her name is Angeli Rose Gomez, a farm supervisor that drove 40 miles to the school.⁣
⁣
Police then ARRESTED HER. Put her in handcuffs. When she demanded that they intervene and save the kids. ⁣
⁣
She convinced someone to take the cuffs off.⁣
⁣
Then ignored their warnings and barriers, marched into the school, and got her two kids.⁣
⁣
All while police sat on their asses and did NOTHING.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Y1wEOX1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Interesting Fact.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/JVJpiPI</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BhZvucm.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Lavinia Ellen "Vinnie" Ream Hoxie (September 25, 1847 – November 20, 1914) was an American sculptor. Her most famous work is the statue of U.S. President Abraham Lincoln in the U.S. Capitol rotunda.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/JVJpiPI</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Ice2Ice2]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Tell me again this isn't a mental illness...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/jaS2qqq</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7rGbarz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/10eC8jl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uUQjAko.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5xtaBkJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aigQo9L.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GQJhgIk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YbwuYra.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7isdu6B.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rX5OLtv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i